:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T23:33:11.000Z","msg":"就算知左死因 你智死得舒服啲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人係自私 真係愛你就唔會捨得推走你講分手<br />\n<br />\n佢一早都知自己嘅家景 又唔見一齊開始果時會介意比唔到咩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意你唔捨得都要分手<br />\n愛你就要放生你 <br />\n等你去搵到自己嘅幸福。<br />\n真係睇戲睇上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩厭左 覺得大家唔啱咪扮聖人mood<br />\n又留番條後路比自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0aede546165a67c4361d2d5b7bef7585205d83","tid":123353,"uid":44833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T23:35:26.000Z","msg":"繼續沉醉係入面喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c308d1e061d1054382e04ae624dd966e3b400f0f","tid":123353,"uid":44833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T23:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算知左死因 你智死得舒服啲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人係自私 真係愛你就唔會捨得推走你講分手<br />\n<br />\n佢一早都知自己嘅家景 又唔見一齊開始果時會介意比唔到咩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意你唔捨得都要分手<br />\n愛你就要放生你 <br />\n等你去搵到自己嘅幸福。<br />\n真係睇戲睇上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">玩厭左 覺得大家唔啱咪扮聖人mood<br />\n又留番條後路比自己 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打講得好岩，鐘意到要分手聽到依句就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04d3f04f16dfa5eac27093a93f769f6344b8365","tid":123353,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T23:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好累人，搵個比到物質嘅人嫁撚左佢算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係係到諗 呢個係事實定係籍囗 定係佢覺得我唔會同佢捱</blockquote><br />\n點睇都係你自己都覺得唔可以同佢捱。自己都無心，如果你真心同佢一齊，請埋佢食又點話。"},{"pid":"47a3e45d0e33cf82303ee45c871e3ae8a7496f3c","tid":123353,"uid":58294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-